<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Mausam</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body>
    {{>header}}
    <div class="relative h-screen">
        <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover blur brightness-50" src="images/about-bg.jpg" alt="hero-img">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
            <div class="p-10 w-2/3 text-center rounded-3xl">
                <h1 class="font-semibold text-5xl text-orange-600 drop-shadow-[1px_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]">About MAUSAM</h1>
                <p class="my-5 font-medium text-2xl text-white drop-shadow-[1px_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-orange-600">MAUSAM</span> is a weather information application for Indian cities.<br>
                    Know more about your city's weather using this web application now!
                </p>
                <p class="my-5 font-medium text-2xl text-white drop-shadow-[1px_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">
                    It was built using TailwindCSS (frontend) &amp; NodeJS, ExpressJS (backend).<br>
                    Enjoy using the app!
                </p>
                <hr class="m-auto w-1/2">
                <h1 class="my-5 font-bold text-3xl text-emerald-400 drop-shadow-[1px_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]">CREDITS</h1>
                <p class="my-3 font-medium text-2xl text-black">
                    Homepage Background Image: Photo by <a href="https://unsplash.com/@noaa?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText" class="font-semibold transition-all hover:text-emerald-400">NOAA</a> on <a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/MPDBY8VELAE?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText" class="font-semibold transition-all hover:text-emerald-400">Unsplash</a>
                    <br>
                    About Page Background Image: <a href="https://www.pexels.com/photo/white-clouds-531767/" class="font-semibold transition-all hover:text-emerald-400">Photo</a> by <a href="https://www.pexels.com/@pixabay/" class="font-semibold transition-all hover:text-emerald-400">Pixabay</a> on <a href="https://www.pexels.com/" class="font-semibold transition-all hover:text-emerald-400">Pexels</a>
                    <br>
                    Weather Page Background Image: Photo by <a href="https://unsplash.com/@alex_gruber?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText" class="font-semibold transition-all hover:text-emerald-400">Alex Gruber</a> on <a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/xrXk5RizL7o?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText" class="font-semibold transition-all hover:text-emerald-400">Unsplash</a>
